  category: string - (optional) standard error category. Default: Unknown correlationId: string - (optional) unique transaction id used to trace execution through the call chain. code: string - (optional) unique error code. Default: &ldquo;UNKNOWN&rdquo; message: string - (optional) human-readable description of the error.  Creates a new instance of ApplicationException.
