Extends: LambdaClient
Description The TestLambdaClient class allows you to create an AWS Lambda client that can be used for automated testing.
Constructors Creates an instance of this class.
 public constructor()
 Instance methods call Calls a remote action in AWS Lambda function. The name of the action is added as &ldquo;cmd&rdquo; parameter to the action parameters.
