  cmd: string - action name to be called. correlationId: string - (optional) transaction id used to trace execution through the call chain. params: any - (optional) action parameters. returns: Promise&lt;any&gt; - action result.  callOneWay Calls an AWS Lambda Function action asynchronously without waiting for the response.
